Skill: fcall       Timer: Support      GL:  5    Cost: 100
This skill will call your Armsman to your side. You will have to RECRUIT an
Armsman, first, though. This is done at the pub north of the room with the
guild board. You will name your Armsman at this time. Be sure it is something
easy to type, as you need to address your Armsman by name to command it.
Additionally, you won't be able to name your Armsman the same as an existing
player, or something offensive.

If for some reason your Armsman stops following you, typing fcall again
should restart the poor git's heart. Remember, after you log out, you
will have to go and track your Armsman down to fcall it again. They love
to hang out at the pub.

If you decide to dual-guild, you will no longer be able to call your
Armsman to help you.

Syntax is: fcall
